#: .\effects.json
msgid "Slowed falls"
msgstr "缓落"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Slowed falls'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You should be able to walk away from most falls unscathed now."
msgstr "你现在应能从大多数坠落中安然无恙地走开。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Slowed falls'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your wings are spread and ready to slow your fall."
msgstr "你的翅膀已展开，准备减缓坠落速度。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Slowed falls'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your wings tuck away."
msgstr "你的翅膀收拢起来。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Fleet-footed serum"
msgid_plural "Fleet-footed serums"
msgstr[0] "迅足血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fleet-footed serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will make you a little faster on flat surfaces."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。此血清将使你在平坦地面上移动得更快一些。"

