#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Plant threshold serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. This one "
"will adapt your body to a more plant-like state permanently if your body "
"supports such a change."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。如果你的身体支持此类变化，此血清将使你的身体永久适应更类似植物的状态。"

