msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得如鲨鱼般锋利的牙齿，并频繁脱落和替换。"

#: .\item.json
msgid "Fast reflexes serum"
msgid_plural "Fast reflexes serums"
msgstr[0] "快速反射血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fast reflexes serum'}
#: .\item.json
msgid ""
"A special mutagenic serum designed to give you a single mutation. Gain "
"faster reflexes and improve your dodging."
msgstr "一种特殊的诱变血清，旨在赋予你单一突变。获得更快的反射速度并提升闪避能力。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Targeted Mutations"
msgstr "定向突变"

#. ~ Description for Targeted Mutations
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds the ability to make serums that will give you one specific mutation, as"
" well as introducing a recipe for making the targeted purifier. I've chosen "
"to only give a few bad mutations targeted mutation serums, as anyone using "
"this likely wants to avoid bad mutations like the plague. Does not support "
"mutations added by other mods, but it's not hard for modders to add the same"
" sort of thing to their own mod. Post-threshold mutations still require you "
"to be past its respective threshold, and if you're capable of reaching the "
"mutation but it's several layers of mutations away you might not get there "
"in one shot. If used and nothing happens or you get the yearning to be free "
"message then it means you cannot get it currently or it is post-threshold. "
"If you want to pass a threshold without risk of other mutations there are "
"serums for that too but you'll need enough mutations in that line to pass it"
" regardless. For an easier time of getting the mutations required to pass a "
"threshold or get more advanced mutations, consult the wiki's mutations page."
" Compatibility with other mods that modify vanilla mutations is unlikely. As"
" a little bonus I've snuck in an ability for some wings that didn't before "
"to slow your fall to safe levels like the bird wings after activating them, "
"which includes the bat, butterfly, and insect wings."
msgstr ""
"新增了制造能赋予你特定突变的血清的能力，并引入了制作定向净化剂的配方。我选择只为少数不良突变提供定向突变血清，因为使用此功能的人很可能想避开不良突变，如同躲避瘟疫。不支持其他模组添加的突变，但模组制作者为自己的模组添加类似功能并不困难。阈值后突变仍要求你超越其相应阈值，如果你有能力达到该突变，但它距离你还有几层突变之遥，你可能无法一次性获得。如果使用后无事发生或你收到“渴望自由”的消息，则意味着你目前无法获得它，或者它是阈值后突变。如果你想无风险地跨越阈值，也有相应的血清，但无论如何你都需要该突变线上足够的突变才能跨越。要更轻松地获得跨越阈值或获得更高级突变所需的突变，请查阅维基的突变页面。与修改原版突变的其他模组兼容的可能性不大。作为一个小彩蛋，我悄悄为一些之前不具备此功能的翅膀添加了能力，在激活后能像鸟翼一样减缓你的下落速度至安全水平，包括蝙蝠、蝴蝶和昆虫翅膀。"

